          <a href="https://docs.bws.ninja/marketplace-solutions/bws.nft.gamecube" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fan Game Cube</a> transforms how fans connect with sports by letting them own virtual zones of real playing fields through NFTs linked to live in-game events. When action unfolds in owned zones—whether it's a game-winning goal or a crucial play—fans earn points and engagement rewards in real time.
        </p>
        <p>
