        </p>
        <p>
          Beyond points, the NFT mechanics enable fans to trade zones on secondary markets, with high-value field positions commanding premium prices. This economic layer adds strategic depth to the ownership experience while generating ongoing engagement throughout entire seasons, keeping fans invested long after individual matches end.
        </p>

